text: Ceroplesis scorteccii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Breuning in 1940. It is known from Ethiopia.BioLib.cz - Ceroplesis scorteccii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Ceroplesini Category:Beetles described in 1940
